; NAME:
;       ANNOTATEINTERACTION::ALIGNGUI, event
;
; PURPOSE:
;
;       This method builds a modal dialog for obtaining user input for
;       how to align selected items.
;
; SYNTAX:
;
;       theObject -> AlignGUI, event
;
; ARGUMENTS:
;
;       event:    The event structure.
;
